/JuliaPackaging/Yggdrasil/pull/9371 to I'll repeat it here:

I think we can ensure OpenSSL finds its certificates and more by setting environment variables: That is, ensure `OPENSSL_CONF`, `OPENSSL_ENGINES`, `OPENSSL_MODULES` are set suitably (see [this issue](https://github.com/openssl/openssl/issues/20644) for more info) by the JLL wrapper, as discussed [here](https://github.com/JuliaPackaging/BinaryBuilder.jl/issues/687) for other packages.

