{"action":"created","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319/events","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/56319","id":2612047090,"node_id":"PR_kwDOABkWpM5_zEYN","number":56319,"title":"Put `jl_gc_new_weakref` in a header file again","user":{"login":"lgoettgens","id":26390525,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2MzkwNTI1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26390525?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens","html_url":"https://github.com/lgoettgens","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lgoettgens/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":195227131,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxOTUyMjcxMzE=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/GC","name":"GC","color":"2CD3F0","default":false,"description":"Garbage collector"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2024-10-24T16:17:36Z","updated_at":"2024-10-28T12:31:22Z","closed_at":"2024-10-24T20:43:27Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/56319","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/56319","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/56319.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/56319.patch","merged_at":"2024-10-24T20:43:27Z"},"body":"The gcext implementation in [gap](https://github.com/gap-system/gap/)/[GAP.jl](https://github.com/oscar-system/GAP.jl) uses `jl_gc_new_weakref`. Since https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55608 got merged, this symbol is no longer mentioned in any header file, and thus the compilation of gap fails. This PR puts it back into a header file, but now in `gc-common.h` (instead of `gc-interface.h`), since https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55608 moved the implementation to `gc-common.c`.

We are aware of the alternative function `jl_gc_new_weakref_th` (that still is in a header after https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55608). However, it was not present in any header file before https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55256, even though it was already marked as `JL_DLLEXPORT` well before that.

In short, without this PR we are not able to adapt the code to a way that works both with julia 1.11 and nightly.

@fingolfin I get locally still the same error as we can observe in CI. I suppose that this needs a rebuild of `libjulia` with this PR here included to work, right? 

ping @d-netto @gbaraldi","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2441460187","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/56319#issuecomment-2441460187","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/56319","id":2441460187,"node_id":"IC_kwDOABkWpM6Rhbnb","user":{"login":"fingolfin","id":241512,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0MTUxMg==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/241512?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin","html_url":"https://github.com/fingolfin","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fingolfin/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2024-10-28T12:31:20Z","updated_at":"2024-10-28T12:31:20Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"Unfortunately this is not quite enough, as just `#include "julia.h"` still won't make this function visible again: Apparently `julia.h` only includes `src/gc-interface.h` but not `src/gc-common.h`. ","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2441460187/reac